<script>
  (function() {
    console.log("[ven session] Getting....");
    //get ven_session using venraaspt.js
    var ven_session = venraastool.getcookie("vensession");
    if (ven_session == "") {
      var url_session = "https://" + venstrob.strserver + venstrob.struuidapi + "?id=" + top.location.host + "&typ=s&pt=a";
      var xhr_session = venraastool.xhr();
      //console.log("[ven session] xhr_session");
      xhr_session.open("GET", url_session, true);
      xhr_session.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=UTF-8");
      xhr_session.withCredentials = true;
      xhr_session.onreadystatechange = function() {
        try {
          if (this.readyState == 4 && this.status == 200) {
            venraastool.doCookieSetup("vensession", this.responseText, 1800000);
            ven_session = this.responseText;
            console.log("[ven session] ven_session=" + ven_session);
            dataLayer.push({
              "ven_weblog.ven_session": ven_session,
              "event": "venGuid"
            });
          }
        }
        catch(e) {}
      };
      xhr_session.send();
    }
    else {
      console.log("[ven session] ven_session=" + ven_session);
      dataLayer.push({
        "ven_weblog.ven_session": ven_session,
        "event": "venGuid"
      });
    }
  })();
</script>

<script>
  function ven_init(token, domain) {
    try {
      console.log("[ven init] venraaspt loading...");

      var venraas_dt = Math.floor((new Date()).getTime() / 86400000);
      var venraas_script = document.createElement("script");
      venraas_script.src = "https://venraas.github.io/demo/GTM/lib/venraaspt.min.js?_=" + venraas_dt; // TODO: 請後續對應GCP環境的 domain name
      venraas_script.async = true;

      venraas_script.onload = venraas_script.onreadystatechange = function() {
        try {
          if ((venraas_script_done == false) &&
              ((this.readyState === "loaded") || (this.reradyState === "complete") || (!this.readyState))) {
            venraas_script_done = true;
            venraas_script.onload = venraas_script.onreadystatechange = null;

            console.log("[ven init] venraaspt loading finished!");

            //網頁載入時要做的事情
            ven_uid();
            ven_device();

            dataLayer.push({
              "ven_weblog.token" : token,
              "ven_weblog.client_host" : domain,
              "ven_weblog.para" : location.search,
              "ven_weblog.uri" : location.pathname,
              "ven_weblog.tophost" : top.location.host,
              "ven_weblog.referrer" : document.referrer,
              "event" : "venSession"
            });
          }
        }
        catch(e) { console.log(e); }
      };

      var head = document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0];
      if (head) {
        head.appendChild(venraas_script);
      }
    }
    catch(e) { console.log("[ven_init]" + e); }
  }

  //頁面瀏覽紀錄
  function ven_portal() {
    //首頁
    ven_log("pageload", "p");
  }
  function ven_category() {
    //分類頁面
    ven_categ_code();
    ven_log("pageload", "cap");
  }
  function ven_good() {
    //商品頁面
    ven_keyword();
    ven_categ_code();
    ven_gid();
    ven_from_rec();
    ven_log("pageload", "gop");
  }
  function ven_edm() {
    //edm頁面
    ven_log("pageload", "edm");
  }
  function ven_search() {
    //搜尋頁面
    ven_keyword();
    ven_log("pageload", "sep");
  }
  function ven_cart(trans_i) {
    //購物車頁面
    ven_trans_i(trans_i);
    ven_log("cartload", "scp");
  }
  function ven_order(trans_i) {
    //結帳頁面
    ven_trans_i(trans_i);
    ven_log("checkout", "orp");
  }
  function ven_log(action, page_type) {
    //自訂頁面
    dataLayer.push(
      {
    	"ven_weblog.action": action,
	    "ven_weblog.page_type": page_type,
        "event": "venWeblog"
      }
    );
  }
  
  //venraas recomd
  //recPos : p, cap, gop...
  //recType : AlsoView, ClickStream
  //rowItems : 推薦商品數量
  //recomdCallback : 呼叫推薦功能後, 所呼叫的function. 如：recomdCallback(jsonStr);
  function ven_recomd(recPos, recType, rowItems, recomdCallback) {
    //呼叫推薦
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_recomd.rec_pos": recPos,
      "ven_recomd.rec_type": recType,
      "ven_recomd.topk": rowItems,
      "ven_recomd.callback": recomdCallback,
      "event" : "venRecomd"
    });
  }


  //其他需要使用之函數
  function getUrlParameter(name) {
    name = name.replace(/[\[]/, '\\[').replace(/[\]]/, '\\]');
    var regex = new RegExp('[\\?&]' + name + '=([^&#]*)');
    var results = regex.exec(window.location.href);
    return results === null ? '' : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\+/g, ' '));
  }
  
  //venraas device
  function ven_device() {
    //讀取使用者瀏覽網頁的裝置(如:pc, mb,...)
    var locationUrl = window.location.toLocaleString();
    var _device = "pc";
    if (locationUrl.indexOf('https://m.') != -1) {
      _device = "mb";
    }

    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_weblog.device": _device
    });
  }

  //venraas get user id if user had login
  function ven_uid() {
    //如果使用者已經登入,讀取user id(uid)
    //此範例為uid在url中帶入
    //uid=xxxxxx
    /*
    var url = new URL(location.href);
    if (getUrlParameter("uid") != '') {
      dataLayer.push({
        "ven_weblog.uid": url.searchParams.get("uid")
      });
    }
    */
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_weblog.uid": "venraaspt.gtm"
    });
  }

  //venraas keyword if web page is search page or good page
  function ven_keyword() {
    //搜尋頁:傳入搜尋keyword；商品頁:若前一頁是從搜尋結果點過來的，傳入搜尋keyword
    //此範例為keyword在url中帶入
    //search=xxxxxx
    var value = getUrlParameter("search");
    if (value != '') {
      dataLayer.push({
        "ven_weblog.keyword": value
      });
    }
  }

  //venraas categ_code if web page is category page
  function ven_categ_code() {
    //當在分類頁面時,抓取分類代碼
    //此範例為cid在url中帶入
    //cid=xxxxxx
    var value = getUrlParameter("cid");
    if (value != '') {
      dataLayer.push({
        "ven_weblog.categ_code": value
      });
    }
  }

  //venraas from_rec if web page is goods page
  function ven_from_rec() {
    //當在商品頁面時,抓取前頁推薦代碼
    //此範例為from_rec在url中帶入
    //from_rec=xxxxxxxxxx
    var value = getUrlParameter("from_rec");
    if (value != '') {
      dataLayer.push({
        "ven_weblog.from_rec": value
      });
    }
  }

  //venraas gid if web page is goods page
  function ven_gid() {
    //當在商品頁面時,抓取商品代碼
    //此範例為gid在url中帶入
    //pid=xxxxxxx
    var value = getUrlParameter("pid");
    if (value != '') {
      dataLayer.push({
        "ven_weblog.gid": value
      });
    }
  }

  //venraas trans_i for 購物車頁面,訂單/結帳頁面
  function ven_trans_i(trans_i) {
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_weblog.trans_i": trans_i
    });
  }

  //venraas ref_info for 購物車頁面
  function ven_ref_info(ref_info) {
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_recomd.ref_info": ref_info
    });
  }

  //venraas w_categ_info
  function ven_w_categ_info(w_categ_info) {
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_recomd.w_categ_info": w_categ_info
    });
  }

  //venraas cartAdd for 商品頁面
  //將商品放入購物車時呼叫
  function ven_cartAdd(gid) {
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_weblog.gid": gid,
      "event" : "venCartAdd"
    });
  }

  (function() {
    //ven_init(token, domain);
    //token : venraas提供的token
    //domain : 網站主要domain
    ven_init("xVtZLw5p4n", "venraas.github.io"); // TODO: 請後續對應 VenRaaS Console 公司設定
  })();

  //venraas_script_done用來判斷venraaspt是否已經載入
  var venraas_script_done = false;
</script>

<script>
  (function() {
    //if found function venraasJob, execute it.
    if (typeof venraasJob === "function") {
      console.log("[ven job] found venraasJob, execute it!");
      venraasJob();
    }
  })();
</script>

<script>
  function ven_recomd_reccall(jsonStr) {
    var recomdCallback = {{ven callback}};
  
    //recCall
    dataLayer.push({
      "ven_recomd.response": jsonStr,
      "event": "venRecCall"
    });

    recomdCallback(jsonStr);
  }

  (function() {
    var recomdParam = {};
    recomdParam.token = {{ven token}};
    recomdParam.rec_pos = {{ven rec_pos}};
    recomdParam.rec_type = {{ven rec_type}};
    recomdParam.uid = {{ven uid}};
    recomdParam.gid = {{ven gid}};
    recomdParam.device = {{ven device}};
    recomdParam.categ_code = {{ven categ_code}};
    recomdParam.topk = {{ven topk}};
    //購物車頁才會有此參數(ref_info)
    if ((recomdParam.rec_pos == "scp") || (recomdParam.rec_pos == "favor")) {
      recomdParam.ref_info = {{ven ref_info}};
    }
    recomdParam.w_categ_info = {{ven w_categ_info}};
    console.log("[ven recomd] recomdParam=" + JSON.stringify(recomdParam));
    venraastool.recomd(recomdParam, ven_recomd_reccall);
  })();
</script>
